description: Creates or updates a Private DNS zone. Does not modify Links to virtual networks or DNS records within the zone.

if_none_match.description: Set to '*' to allow a new Private DNS zone to be created, but to prevent updating an existing zone. Other values will be ignored.

subscription_id.description: Gets subscription credentials which uniquely identify Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group.

private_zone_name.description: The name of the Private DNS zone (without a terminating dot).

parameters.description: Parameters supplied to the CreateOrUpdate operation.

if_match.description: The ETag of the Private DNS zone. Omit this value to always overwrite the current zone. Specify the last-seen ETag value to prevent accidentally overwriting any concurrent changes.
